txt.en: Burned slop piles at Baur Kasak.
Slop piles can be found at Baur Kasak in Arandor.\n\nYou should burn slop piles at Baur Kasak.

You burned many piles of the disgusting slop found among the Warg dens of Baur Kasak, depriving the creatures of many stomach-wrenching meals. To your disgust, you find that you can still smell the burning slop, and you hope only that the odour will have faded by dinnertime.
Within each crack and crevasse of the hills at Baur Kasak, Wargs feast on disease-ridden piles of mangled flesh. You should burn this vile food, if food it can be called.
Slop piles can be found at Baur Kasak in Arandor.\n\nYou should burn slop piles at Baur Kasak.
The Warg dens of Baur Kasak are a dangerous place to venture, but if the Great Alliance is to have victory, they must be dared.
